# contains(_:)

**Instance Method**

Indicates whether the receiver contains the specified date.

## Declaration

```swift
func contains(_ date: Date) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **date**: The date for which to test membership of the date interval.

## Return Value

[doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] if the receiver contains `date`. Otherwise, [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false].
